lead_paragraph: Britain's double Olympic champion cyclist Laura Trott says she is not worried about the Zika virus, which has led to a number of athletes withdrawing from the Rio Games.

headline.print_headline: Trott Unfazed by Zika Fears Ahead of Rio Games
